<h2>Methodology</h2>

<p>Organization names from the raw Flock spreadsheet were normalized by extracting state codes, stripping common suffixes (PD, SO, Sheriff's Office, etc.), and lowercasing. Only rows where SPPD is actively sharing data (<code>Networks I'm Sharing</code> is non-null) are counted.</p>

